-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>8</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>6.</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"209\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Анна-Марія Турковська</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"85\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>7</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>7.</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"209\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Оля Кузнецова</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"85\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>7</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>8.</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"209\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Софія Коротушак</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"85\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>6</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>9.</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"209\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Софія Пруцька</strong></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"85\">\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong